mil.nga.giat.geowave.format.geotools.vector

Class GeoToolsVectorDataStoreIngestFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.giat.geowave.format.geotools.vector.GeoToolsVectorDataStoreIngestFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IngestFormatPluginProviderSpi<Object,org.opengis.feature.simple.SimpleFeature>

    public class GeoToolsVectorDataStoreIngestFormat
extends Object
implements IngestFormatPluginProviderSpi<Object,org.opengis.feature.simple.SimpleFeature>
    This represents an ingest format plugin provider for GeoTools vector data stores. It currently only supports ingesting data directly from a local file system into GeoWave.
